description.en: WenMoon is a community based meme token. Since the inception of Bitcoin the question, "WenMoon?" has been countless number of times. Now we become the SOLUTION! WenMoon is a deflationary token with 5% reflection to marketing and 2% reflection to holders. The token will be used in the future for a P2E Space game in which holders will be able to compete against each other and wager their tokens for the opportunity to win more.
